@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_krtddp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (v1 - (wp.abs(v1 + 0.05) / (v1 + 0.83 + tmp + 0.33)))
    v1 = wp.cos((wp.exp(v2 + 0.72) * (v0 + 0.21 + v1 + 0.13)))
    v0 = 0.36
    v0 = v2
    v2 = (wp.abs((v2 + 0.28 / v0 + 0.11)) / 0.48)
    v0 = 0.86
    v2 = v0
    v0 = 0.57
    data[tid] = v0
